Class IconScan<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uidaho.junicon.runtime.junicon.iterators.IconIterator<T>
      • edu.uidaho.junicon.runtime.junicon.iterators.IconComposition<T>
        • edu.uidaho.junicon.runtime.junicon.constructs.IconScan<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IIconComposition<T>, IIconIterator<T>, Iterable<T>, Runnable, Callable<T>, Iterator<T>

    public class IconScan<T>
extends IconComposition<T>
    Create string scanning environment for scan operator text?expr. Associated within the scope of each operation is a scan environment. This scan environment is a thread local that must be saved and restored on exit and re-entry to the scan operator, either on iteration or on suspend and resume.
